{
  "stem": "17526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There were selections afterwards, but I'll forget this selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were trying to huddle together, and at night the first day, the first night, there was a downpour and everybody was just sitting on the ground getting soaking wet while they were taking a break of the selection.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "During the daytime the next morning, the selection started again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was just a simple nod with the thumb, left and right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Left, you were loaded on trucks and the trucks were hauling away the people, and the right you were separated from families.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There hardly has been one family that did not lose anybody in this selection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There were older people that were immediately shown to the left, there were young kids-- kids were taken away from their mothers and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the screaming and the panic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "No food, no water, two days or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "After two or two and a half days, when the selection was finished, those people that were selected to be alive were finally let go and there was not a house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And as we came home and we heard the screamings from our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We, fortunately, were lucky to be the whole, our whole family coming back, all five of us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But not one neighbor didn't left-- didn't lose anybody at this selection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we know very well, we had no illusions about it, although all kinds of rumors were circulating at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And there were obviously false rumors that these people are being resettled.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
